    "description": "Play with up to 10 players online, venture deep into the Mapinguari's Temple and collect all <strong>three hidden artifacts</strong> to ensure a successful expedition! Be careful, however, for not only a dreaded monster roams the Temple's corridors but also an amalgam of deadly traps and a deceitful cultist, disguised between you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745640/extras/131c22f205f6ff6bdbbc9c0ca22c0fac.avif?t=1761568015\" width=384 height=144 /></span><br><strong>Explorers:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Win by collecting all the <strong>three idols</strong> hidden inside the dungeon.<br></li><li> Talk to nearby players (or using the radio) to coordinate the exploration.<br></li><li> Find the lost gun so the bodyguard isn't alone defending you comrades, and do it before the cultist finds it first.<br></li><li> move items around, such as keys or barrels, and solve the puzzles scattered throughout the dungeon.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745640/extras/3fe18f6e6a2d550eeb69ad5f02c709b3.avif?t=1761568015\" width=384 height=144 /></span><br><strong>Cultist:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Summon the Mapinguari so it may hunt down your enemies (be careful, he may kill you as well).<br></li><li> Be the last one alive to win the game!<br></li><li> Use tricks such as turning off all the lights, blocking paths with objects, or stealing and hiding the idols!!<br></li><li> Find the <strong>lost gun</strong> to slow down or even kill the other players.<br></li><li> Travel the dungeon quickly through secret passages only you can access.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745640/extras/691f3a91477f0aa043084ae5832e0aa3.avif?t=1761568015\" width=384 height=144 /></span><br><strong>Bodyguard:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Be the judge, jury and executioner, as only you starts the game with a gun.<br></li><li> Be careful, for everyone knows who the bodyguard is.<br></li><li> Protect the explorers and hunt down the cultist.<br></li><li> Slow down the <strong>monster</strong> with your bullets.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745640/extras/736b072e02bfba2a19e4e72686d5a854.avif?t=1761568015\" width=512 height=128 /></span><br><strong>MACE: Mapinguari's Temple</strong> is a game where you can:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Talk in-game with other players, either by proximity or usign the <strong>radio</strong> function.<br></li><li> Customize your experience: not up for a competitive game? Play without a cultist and transform the game into a group horror game.<br></li><li> Choose a character to play and customize it by changing it's colors!<br></li><li> Play with <strong>accessibility features</strong>, such as high contrast.<br></li><li> Find any match quickly by searching the server list!</li></ul>",
